{
  "name": "1999pr~1-c5516b",
  "title": "Aberdeen's IT Professional Services Practice \u2014 Coverage Areas",
  "description": "This document describes Aberdeen Group's IT Professional Services practice structure and coverage areas as of January 1999, organized in a matrix by market initiative and supplier type. It identifies four key market segments\u2014Windows 2000 infrastructure, ERP/Supply Chain, Customer Information Systems, and Education\u2014and provides a detailed vendor landscape for each. The document concludes with a sample IBM Global Services profile illustrating Aberdeen's analyst methodology.",
